title: AG Women's Adria Low Rise Baggy Wide Leg in Gallery White
description: The Adria Low Rise Baggy Wide Leg hangs on the hip for a slouchy, relaxed look. The fit is relaxed in the hip, wide in the leg and meant to puddle at the hem for that effortless, off duty vibe.
